        "timestamp": 1699144294
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The statement seems a bit redundant: instead of <code>‚àÄ N ‚â• N‚ÇÄ, ‚àÄ s ‚äÜ {n | N ‚â§ n}</code> it's equivalent to say <code>‚àÄ s ‚äÜ {n | N‚ÇÄ ‚â§ n}</code>.</p>",
        "id": 400338750,
